        "layout": "right",
        "image_text_heading": "THINKERS, DESIGNERS, COLLABORATORS.",
        "content": "At Vanguard Store Fixtures, we take pride in having the capabilities of outfitting a retail store from start to finish—regardless of its size. Our Canadian-manufactured gondola shelving, custom millwork, and precision metal-fabricated products, combined with strong partnerships with North America’s most trusted food equipment brands, distinguish us in the industry.\n\nWhether you're launching a new store or revitalizing an existing one, our experienced team ensures your space is set up with the highest quality fixtures and equipment in the most efficient and strategic layout. Through detailed floor plans and 3D renderings, we guarantee your store will match expectations—down to the finest detail.\n\nPartnering with us means more than just accessing premium products; it means gaining peace of mind. Our comprehensive, end-to-end solutions are tailored to your unique retail needs, supported by expert guidance every step of the way. With a commitment to quality, innovation, and seamless execution, Vanguard ensures your store is not only fully equipped but also optimized for customer experience and sales performance.\n\nTrust us to bring your retail vision to life—with precision, reliability, and excellence."
      }
