          "type": "store",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/floor-plan-size-icon.png",
            "slider-heading": "Store Planning",
            "desc": "<p>Our store planning process is a vital first step toward realizing your retail vision. It involves meticulous attention to detail and the creation of 2D and 3D drawings that provide a comprehensive layout of the retail space. By laying down a solid foundation, we ensure a well-organized, efficient, and customer-friendly environment that perfectly aligns with your brand.</p>",
            "btn_text": "Learn more",
            "btn_link": "#"
          }
        },
        "148aa6e8-f120-456c-a461-ca08c0007453": {
          "type": "store",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/architectural-icon.png",
            "slider-heading": "Interior Design",
            "desc": "<p>The aesthetic part of your brand comes to life in the interior design phase. We focus on creating a visually appealing environment that encapsulates your brand ethos. Our design professionals select colors, materials, and finishes that not only elevate the customer experience but also align with your brand message, creating a cohesive and inviting ambiance.</p>",
            "btn_text": "Learn more",
            "btn_link": "#"
          }
        },
        "a78580d4-2401-449d-a9ea-42834094f183": {
          "type": "store",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/manufacturing-production-icon.png",
            "slider-heading": "Manufacturing Process:",
            "desc": "<p>Our manufacturing process is an intricate blend of quality and customization. From store fixtures to custom millwork and metal fabrication, each component is manufactured to the highest standards of quality. We employ cutting-edge technology and skilled craftsmen to ensure that every piece we produce is functional, durable, and perfectly in tune with your store's design.</p>",
            "btn_text": "Learn more",
            "btn_link": "#"
          }
        },
        "d4958ac9-fffd-490f-9bce-f9ec7cbab404": {
          "type": "store",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/toolbox-repairing-icon.png",
            "slider-heading": "Delivery & Installation:",
            "desc": "<p>We understand that time is of the essence in the retail world, so we ensure a smooth delivery and installation process. Our expert team handles each aspect meticulously, from logistics to on-site assembly. The fixtures arrive safely, are assembled with precision, and are thoroughly inspected to ensure that they align with your store's planned design and functionality.</p>",
            "btn_text": "Learn more",
            "btn_link": "#"
          }
        },
        "07feebbe-98d5-428e-8f3a-cc1630ed2b79": {
          "type": "store",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/guarantee-icon.png",
            "slider-heading": "Guaranteed Satisfaction",
            "desc": "<p>Customer satisfaction is our ultimate goal and number one priority. We stand behind the quality of our work and offer comprehensive post-installation support. If for any reason you’re not completely satisfied, we commit to making it right. Our mission is to deliver a retail environment that not only meets but exceeds your expectations, ensuring your business thrives.</p>",
            "btn_text": "Learn more",
            "btn_link": "#"
